1. Fix Ownership for all Mounts

Run this single block to make yourself the owner of all the drives you just added to fstab:
Bash

sudo chown -R omkar:omkar /media/sdb1
sudo chown -R omkar:omkar /media/sdb2
sudo chown -R omkar:omkar /media/sdb3
sudo chown -R omkar:omkar /media/sda3
sudo chown -R omkar:omkar /media/sda4
sudo chown -R omkar:omkar /media/sda5
